      • execute

        public void execute()
             throws LicenseScoutExecutionException
        Main execution of the LicenseScout.

        This executes:

        1. Reads configuration files:
          1. Reads providers file
          2. Reads notices file
          3. Reads licenses file
          4. Reads URL mappings file
          5. Reads name mappings file
          6. Reads global filters file
          7. Reads checked archives file
          8. Reads filtered vendor names file
        2. Checks parameters
        Throws:
        LicenseScoutExecutionException - if an unrecoverable condition occurs during the execution or if another exception is caught
